<view class="page article-detail" wx:if="{{article}}"><image wx:if="{{article.cover_url}}" class="article-hero" src="{{article.cover_url}}" mode="aspectFill"/><view wx:else class="article-hero hero-fallback">{{article.category_text}}</view><view class="article-head"><text class="article-category">{{article.category_text}}</text><text class="title">{{article.title}}</text><text class="subtitle">{{article.summary}}</text></view><view class="article-body"><text class="paragraph" wx:for="{{article.content}}" wx:key="index">{{item}}</text></view><view class="reference-note">本文用于日常健康管理参考，不替代医疗建议。</view></view>
<view class="loading-state" wx:elif="{{loading}}">正在加载文章...</view><view class="page" wx:else><view class="card empty"><text class="empty-title">文章暂时无法打开</text><text class="muted-text">文章可能已下架，也可以检查网络后重新加载。</text><view class="secondary-button retry" role="button" bindtap="loadArticle">重新加载</view></view></view>
